<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٦٩٦ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا مُسَدَّدٌ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا يَحْيَى، عَنْ شُعْبَةَ، عَنْ أَبِي التَّيَّاحِ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ <span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">(الْبَرَكَةُ فِي نَوَاصِي الْخَيْلِ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
